        <Literal>A reservation for an event like a concert, sporting event, or lecture.&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;

Note: This type is for information about actual reservations, e.g. in confirmation emails or HTML pages with individual confirmations of reservations. For offers of tickets, use &lt;a class=&quot;localLink&quot; href=&quot;http://schema.org/Offer&quot;&gt;Offer&lt;/a&gt;.</Literal>
    </AnnotationAssertion>
