        <Literal>Natural languages such as Spanish, Tamil, Hindi, English, etc. Formal language code tags expressed in &lt;a href=&quot;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/IETF_language_tag&quot;&gt;BCP 47&lt;/a&gt; can be used via the &lt;a class=&quot;localLink&quot; href=&quot;http://schema.org/alternateName&quot;&gt;alternateName&lt;/a&gt; property. The Language type previously also covered programming languages such as Scheme and Lisp, which are now best represented using &lt;a class=&quot;localLink&quot; href=&quot;http://schema.org/ComputerLanguage&quot;&gt;ComputerLanguage&lt;/a&gt;.</Literal>
    </AnnotationAssertion>
    <AnnotationAssertion>
        <AnnotationProperty abbreviatedIRI="rdfs:label"/>
