        <AnnotationProperty abbreviatedIRI="rdfs:comment"/>
        <AbbreviatedIRI>schema1:Observation</AbbreviatedIRI>
        <Literal>Instances of the class &lt;a class=&quot;localLink&quot; href=&quot;http://schema.org/Observation&quot;&gt;Observation&lt;/a&gt; are used to specify observations about an entity (which may or may not be an instance of a &lt;a class=&quot;localLink&quot; href=&quot;http://schema.org/StatisticalPopulation&quot;&gt;StatisticalPopulation&lt;/a&gt;), at a particular time. The principal properties of an &lt;a class=&quot;localLink&quot; href=&quot;http://schema.org/Observation&quot;&gt;Observation&lt;/a&gt; are &lt;a class=&quot;localLink&quot; href=&quot;http://schema.org/observedNode&quot;&gt;observedNode&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a class=&quot;localLink&quot; href=&quot;http://schema.org/measuredProperty&quot;&gt;measuredProperty&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a class=&quot;localLink&quot; href=&quot;http://schema.org/measuredValue&quot;&gt;measuredValue&lt;/a&gt; (or &lt;a class=&quot;localLink&quot; href=&quot;http://schema.org/median&quot;&gt;median&lt;/a&gt;, etc.) and &lt;a class=&quot;localLink&quot; href=&quot;http://schema.org/observationDate&quot;&gt;observationDate&lt;/a&gt; (&lt;a class=&quot;localLink&quot; href=&quot;http://schema.org/measuredProperty&quot;&gt;measuredProperty&lt;/a&gt; properties can, but need not always, be W3C RDF Data Cube &quot;measure properties&quot;, as in the &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.w3.org/TR/vocab-data-cube/#dsd-example&quot;&gt;lifeExpectancy example&lt;/a&gt;).
See also &lt;a class=&quot;localLink&quot; href=&quot;http://schema.org/StatisticalPopulation&quot;&gt;StatisticalPopulation&lt;/a&gt;, and the &lt;a href=&quot;/docs/data-and-datasets.html&quot;&gt;data and datasets&lt;/a&gt; overview for more details.</Literal>
