If the value for the &lt;a class=&quot;localLink&quot; href=&quot;http://schema.org/closes&quot;&gt;closes&lt;/a&gt; property is less than the value for the &lt;a class=&quot;localLink&quot; href=&quot;http://schema.org/opens&quot;&gt;opens&lt;/a&gt; property then the hour range is assumed to span over the next day.</Literal>
    </AnnotationAssertion>
