    <AnnotationAssertion>
        <AnnotationProperty abbreviatedIRI="rdfs:comment"/>
        <AbbreviatedIRI>schema1:TouristTrip</AbbreviatedIRI>
        <Literal>A tourist trip. A created itinerary of visits to one or more places of interest (&lt;a class=&quot;localLink&quot; href=&quot;http://schema.org/TouristAttraction&quot;&gt;TouristAttraction&lt;/a&gt;/&lt;a class=&quot;localLink&quot; href=&quot;http://schema.org/TouristDestination&quot;&gt;TouristDestination&lt;/a&gt;) often linked by a similar theme, geographic area, or interest to a particular &lt;a class=&quot;localLink&quot; href=&quot;http://schema.org/touristType&quot;&gt;touristType&lt;/a&gt;. The &lt;a href=&quot;http://www2.unwto.org/&quot;&gt;UNWTO&lt;/a&gt; defines tourism trip as the Trip taken by visitors.
  (See examples below).</Literal>
    </AnnotationAssertion>
