        <AnnotationProperty abbreviatedIRI="rdfs:comment"/>
        <AbbreviatedIRI>schema1:WarrantyScope</AbbreviatedIRI>
        <Literal>A range of of services that will be provided to a customer free of charge in case of a defect or malfunction of a product.&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;

Commonly used values:&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;http://purl.org/goodrelations/v1#Labor-BringIn&lt;/li&gt;
