        <AbbreviatedIRI>schema1:WebPage</AbbreviatedIRI>
        <Literal>A web page. Every web page is implicitly assumed to be declared to be of type WebPage, so the various properties about that webpage, such as &lt;code&gt;breadcrumb&lt;/code&gt; may be used. We recommend explicit declaration if these properties are specified, but if they are found outside of an itemscope, they will be assumed to be about the page.</Literal>
    </AnnotationAssertion>
