        <Literal>The GTIN-14 code of the product, or the product to which the offer refers. See &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.gs1.org/barcodes/technical/idkeys/gtin&quot;&gt;GS1 GTIN Summary&lt;/a&gt; for more details.</Literal>
    </AnnotationAssertion>
    <AnnotationAssertion>
