Use standard formats: &lt;a href=&quot;http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/ISO_4217&quot;&gt;ISO 4217 currency format&lt;/a&gt; e.g. &quot;USD&quot;; &lt;a href=&quot;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/List_of_cryptocurrencies&quot;&gt;Ticker symbol&lt;/a&gt; for cryptocurrencies e.g. &quot;BTC&quot;; well known names for &lt;a href=&quot;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Local_exchange_trading_system&quot;&gt;Local Exchange Tradings Systems&lt;/a&gt; (LETS) and other currency types e.g. &quot;Ithaca HOUR&quot;.</Literal>
