        <Literal>The &quot;spatial&quot; property can be used in cases when more specific properties
(e.g. &lt;a class=&quot;localLink&quot; href=&quot;http://schema.org/locationCreated&quot;&gt;locationCreated&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a class=&quot;localLink&quot; href=&quot;http://schema.org/spatialCoverage&quot;&gt;spatialCoverage&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a class=&quot;localLink&quot; href=&quot;http://schema.org/contentLocation&quot;&gt;contentLocation&lt;/a&gt;) are not known to be appropriate.</Literal>
    </AnnotationAssertion>
