        <AbbreviatedIRI>schema1:spatialCoverage</AbbreviatedIRI>
        <Literal>The spatialCoverage of a CreativeWork indicates the place(s) which are the focus of the content. It is a subproperty of
      contentLocation intended primarily for more technical and detailed materials. For example with a Dataset, it indicates
